((That was one excellent Vacation!))

::Liono::
Liono slowly places the last few space mines "Void how is the defense Grid?"

::Koj::
Koj wipes the motor oil off his hands and looks a Lion Assault 2 "I'm all 
done over here she should fly."

::Lilly::
Lilly gentle walks up to Koj and inspects his work "Not too bad."
Lilly places her hand on Koj's shoulder gently.

::Void::
Void floating in air back at Cats Lair continues processing the Ark defense 
progress. She lifts her arm and waves it one time creating a view screen 
showing charts of their progress.  "The Ark defense grid is back at 
one-hundred percent the Cats Eye 1 is fully function. The new changes you 
have made will insure the Arks safety. Come back to earth cats."
